ement-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-11b6ceb elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"11b6ceb\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-2b0f771\" data-id=\"2b0f771\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2b88675 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2b88675\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"font-size: 17px; font-style: normal;\"><b>RECOMB CCB and RECOMB Seq 2022<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> invite PhD students and postdocs to submit their expression of interest to participate in a joint session on Scientific Communication with prizes available for best presenters. Communication is an essential skill, required for grant application writing, conference presentations, and journal articles. The purpose of this session is to demonstrate the ability to explain a scientific project in layman\u2019s and jargon-free terms.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">Each student and postdoc participating to the RECOMB-CCB and Seq\u2019s Scientific Communication session will be asked to deliver a jargon-free and lay presentation of 5 minutes with or without the use of visual and media aids (e.g., Powerpoint presentation) covering the concepts:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">\n<li style=\"font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What&nbsp;<\/span>is the main objective?<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Why&nbsp;<\/span>did you do your study (scientific rationale)?<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 17px; font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What<\/span>&nbsp;are the results (if available)?<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-size: 17px; font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What<\/span>&nbsp;happens&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">next<\/span>&nbsp;(or expected to happen next once you have results)?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">Each presentation will be reviewed by a small judging panel. Judging would be based on how clearly the concepts would be understood by a general\/lay audience, with a minimum of scientific jargon. Prizes will be available for the winners (details to be available soon). Presentations will be split into a session dedicated to students that will take place on Saturday 21th at 2.45pm within RECOMB CCB and RECOMB Seq schedule, and a session dedicated to postdocs that will take place the same day at 4pm.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 17px; font-style: normal;\">Please apply by&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">May 15th, 2022<\/span>&nbsp;to join the RECOMB-CCB and Seq\u2019s Scientific Communication session through the track \u201cJoint session RECOMB CCB and Seq\u201d of the&nbsp;<a style=\"font-weight: 400;\" href=\"https:\/\/easychair.org\/my\/conference?conf=recomb2022\">RECOMB 2022 EasyChair server<\/a><span style=\"font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; background-color: var(--ast-global-color-4); color: var(--ast-global-color-3);\">. In the application, please include few words to describe the broad topic of the proposed presentation and related key words. Confirmations will be sent by <\/span><span style=\"font-style: inherit; background-color: var(--ast-global-color-4); color: var(--ast-global-color-3);\"><b>May 18th, 2022<\/b><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; background-color: var(--ast-global-color-4); color: var(--ast-global-color-3);\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/easychair.org\/my\/conference?conf=recomb2022\" style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">https:\/\/easychair.org\/my\/conference?conf=recomb202<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-9812714\" data-id=\"9812714\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fe83983 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fe83983\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div><h4 style=\"font-size: 1.47059rem; font-style: normal;\">Contacts<\/h4><\/div><div>\u00a0Please direct your queries and comments to <a href=\"mailto:recombccb2022@gmail.com\">recombccb2022@gmail .com<\/a><br \/><br \/><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b62718 elementor-shape-rounded elementor-grid-0 e-grid-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-social-icons\" data-id=\"9b62718\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"social-icons.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.7.2 - 21-08-2022 *\/\n.elementor-widget-social-icons.elementor-grid-0 .elementor-widget-container,.elementor-widget-social-icons.elementor-grid-mobile-0 .elementor-widget-container,.elementor-widget-social-icons.elementor-grid-tablet-0 .elementor-widget-container{line-height:1;font-size:0}.elementor-widget-social-icons:not(.elementor-grid-0):not(.elementor-grid-tablet-